      <section eId="sec_1308">
        <num>1308</num>
        <heading>Amendments or changes</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1308__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>An authorized foreign corporation may amend or change its\napplication for authority from time to time in any and as many of the\nfollowing respects as may be desired if the amendments contain only such\nprovisions as might be lawfully contained in an application for\nauthority at the time of making such amendment:\n</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_a__subsec_1">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To change its corporate name if such change has been effected\nunder the laws of the jurisdiction of its incorporation.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_a__subsec_2">
            <num>(2)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To change its fictitious name filed pursuant to paragraph</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1308__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of\nsection 1301 of this chapter, to another fictitious name, if its true\ncorporate name is not available for use in this state.\n</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_d__subsec_3">
            <num>(3)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To delete its fictitious name filed pursuant to paragraph</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1308__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of\nsection 1301 of this chapter, if its true corporate name is now\navailable for use in this state.\n</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_d__subsec_4">
            <num>(4)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To adopt a fictitious name when the corporate name is changed and\nis not available in this state.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_d__subsec_5">
            <num>(5)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To enlarge, limit or otherwise change the business which it\nproposes to do in this state.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_d__subsec_6">
            <num>(6)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To change the location of its office in this state.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_d__subsec_7">
            <num>(7)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To specify or change the post office address to which the\nsecretary of state shall mail a copy of any process against it served\nupon him.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_d__subsec_8">
            <num>(8)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To make, revoke or change the designation of a registered agent or\nto specify or change his address.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_d__subsec_9">
            <num>(9)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To change the jurisdiction of its incorporation if such change has\nbeen effected under laws permitting such a change to occur.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1308__subsec_d__subsec_10">
            <num>(10)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To specify, change or delete the email address to which the\nsecretary of state shall email a notice of the fact that process against\nthe corporation has been electronically served upon him or her.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
      </section>
